description:

Heat Sublimation is beneficial for one off's or smaller orders. The set cost is $12 for a one sided press and $15 for a two sided press.

----> For Heat Sublimation garments must be 100% polyester and light gray or white. 
----> Benefit, no cost per color. Able to have multiple colors for no additional cost.
